Want to leave a special thankyou for Lisa, the house was perfect and clean and easy to get to. Lisa was not only kind anough to let us have a later check out and leave our things there until late afternoon but she also helped us by phoning tje airport and helping us find our lost baggage. She was incredibly helpful without losing her smile at all!
If i come back I will definitly contact Lisa again as she helped us feel very looked after.
title: Eastside Bungalow SXSW/dwntwn
